WEBVTT

00:01.215 --> 00:02.781
Previously on "The Originals"...

00:02.782 --> 00:05.004
Cami: Right now, people like me
are out there getting killed

00:05.005 --> 00:07.108
by people like you,
conveniently timed

00:07.109 --> 00:09.472
with the arrival of
your old acquaintance.

00:09.473 --> 00:12.719
So you came all this way
to deliver a warning.

00:12.720 --> 00:14.611
The life of
every vampire is linked back

00:14.612 --> 00:16.579
to the original
who begat the line.

00:16.580 --> 00:19.147
Kill an original,
wipe out an entire line.

00:19.148 --> 00:21.918
If you want to know what I'd do
about the dangers you now face,

00:21.919 --> 00:24.154
there is something
that you must see.

00:24.155 --> 00:26.255
Your ancient heart
beats strong, indeed,

00:26.257 --> 00:27.891
for someone in such danger.

00:27.892 --> 00:29.659
If you have a warning
to deliver, luv,

00:29.660 --> 00:30.960
best get on with it.

00:30.961 --> 00:33.129
Freya: His prophecy
is fulfilled.

00:33.130 --> 00:35.565
You will all fall...
One by friend,

00:35.566 --> 00:38.735
one by foe, and one by family.

00:38.736 --> 00:40.837
You've acquired
countless enemies,

00:40.838 --> 00:44.114
and with the sire lines at war,
you now have mine, as well.

00:44.115 --> 00:47.106
Anyone who would kill me
could now come after you.

00:47.107 --> 00:50.200
From now on, I am the only one
you can trust.

